author: wn.com
title: Behind Ben Carson's rebellious public image, a DC insider is hard at work
text: NEW YORK (Reuters) - U.S. presidential candidate Ben Carson may be the farthest Republican voters can get from the party's establishment: A retired neurosurgeon with a penchant for inflammatory comments who has never held, much less run, for elected office.
